{"badges":["TM31","TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place bread, spring onion\/shallot and salt into mixing bowl and chop <b>Turbo\/2 sec\/2 times<b>, until fine crumbs form. Transfer into a bowl and set aside.","Place 50 g of the butter into mixing bowl and heat <b>1 min\/90°C\/speed 1<b>.","Add all mushrooms and chop <b>5 sec\/speed 5<b>.","Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula and cook <b>5 min\/90°C\/speed 1<b>.","Add reserved breadcrumb mixture and stir <b>10 sec\/speed 3<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula. Set mixing bowl aside and allow mixture to cool (approx. 15 minutes).","Add cream cheese, nutmeg, lemon juice, pepper and remaining 50 g butter and blend <b>20 sec\/speed 5<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl and lid with spatula.","Add parsley and blend <b>20 sec\/speed 5<b>. Divide mixture between 4 small ramekins (125 ml) or into a large ceramic dish, cover with plastic wrap and place into refrigerator for a minimum of 1 hour. Serve chilled with crackers or crudité."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["25 g day-old bread, roughly torn","1 spring onion\/shallot, trimmed and cut into thirds","½ tsp salt","100 g salted butter, softened and cut into pieces","200 g fresh portobello mushrooms, cut into quarters","100 g fresh brown mushrooms, cut into quarters","100 g fresh shiitake mushrooms, cut into quarters","50 g cream cheese","½ tsp ground nutmeg","1 tsp lemon juice","½ tsp ground black pepper","3 sprigs fresh flat-leaf parsley, leaves only"]}],"id":"r253104","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-zGgCXcbjUq8\/XZadk8HUA4I\/AAAAAAAAgdQ\/lVhv0AULouUHIqB-uHE5NVC8HAUl2pDKACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_Ed3HUMDpgF_e82A1.png","title":"Mixed mushroom pâté","publishedAt":"2018-02-18T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{},"usefulItems":"plastic wrap, bowl, ramekins (125 ml), refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["To make this recipe gluten free, use gluten free bread in step 1."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h 25m","1"]}